performance improvement tips: https://blog.jetbrains.com/pycharm/2025/11/10-smart-performance-hacks-for-faster-python-code/
1: Membership testing with a list (x in some_list) requires scanning each element one by one, time complexity (O(n))
   sets in Python are implemented as hash tables, which allow for constant-time (O(1)) lookups on average.
2: Avoid unnecessary copies 
3: Use __slots__ for memory efficiency :explicitly declare a fixed set of attributes for a class
4: Use math functions instead of operators
5: Pre-allocate memory with known sizes
6: Avoid exception handling in hot loops
7: Use local functions for repeated logic
8: Use itertools for combinatorial operations
9: Use bisect for sorted list operations
10: Avoid repeated function calls in loops

book for data science: https://jakevdp.github.io/PythonDataScienceHandbook/

project package management:
1) python -m venv  .venv
   source .venv/bin/activate
   edit pyproject.toml
      [project]
        name = "project_name"
        version = "0.1.0"
        dependencies = [
          "module==version_name"
        ]
   pip install -e .
2) edit pyproject.toml
      [project]
        name = "project_name"
        version = "0.1.0"
    uv add library_name(depends on)
    publish, co-worker can setup via "uv sync" or "uv run main.py"

uv python list — 列出uv支持的python版本
uv python install cpython3.12 — 安装某个python版本 (3.12)
uv run -p 3.12 xxx.py — 使用特定版本python运行xxx.py
uv run -p 3.12 python — 运行python交互界面
uv run xxx.py— 使用系统python或当前工程的虚拟环境运行xxx.py
uv init — 创建工程
uv add pydantic_ai — 添加依赖 (pydantic_ai)
uv tree — 打印依赖树
uv remove pydantic_ai — 删除依赖
uv build — 编译工程
